---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Customers - AnswerLayer"
  description="How different teams use AnswerLayer to unlock insights from their data."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h1 class="mb-lg">Use Cases</h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-2xl">
        Different teams use AnswerLayer in different ways.
        Here's how our customers are building with the platform.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Persona 1: Enterprise Data Team -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="persona">
        <h2 class="persona-title">Enterprise Data Team</h2>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Challenge</div>
          <p>
            Data analysts drowning in ad-hoc requests. Business users can't get answers
            without filing a ticket and waiting days. Dashboards are static and don't
            answer the follow-up questions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Solution</div>
          <p>
            Deploy AnswerLayer as a self-serve analytics layer. Business users ask questions
            in plain English. The semantic layer ensures consistent definitions across the org.
            PII filtering protects sensitive customer data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Outcome</div>
          <p class="text-muted">
            80% reduction in analyst ticket volume. Time-to-insight drops from days to seconds.
            Data team focuses on high-value projects instead of ad-hoc requests.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Persona 2: AI Product Company -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="persona">
        <h2 class="persona-title">AI Product Company</h2>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Challenge</div>
          <p>
            Building analytics into their SaaS product. Don't want to build and maintain
            a data infrastructure layer. Need to support multiple customer databases
            without exposing raw SQL to the LLM.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Solution</div>
          <p>
            Embed AnswerLayer as the analytics backend. Each customer gets their own
            isolated semantic layer. The API returns structured data that feeds into
            the product's AI features.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Outcome</div>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Shipped AI-powered analytics in 2 weeks instead of 6 months. No database
            infrastructure to maintain. Multi-tenant by default.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Persona 3: Regulated Industry -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="persona">
        <h2 class="persona-title">Regulated Industry</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-lg">Healthcare, Finance, Government</p>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Challenge</div>
          <p>
            Need AI-powered analytics but can't send data to external services.
            Strict compliance requirements around data residency and access controls.
            Must demonstrate audit trails for all data access.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Solution</div>
          <p>
            VPC deploymentâ€”AnswerLayer runs entirely in their cloud. Data never leaves
            their environment. PII filtering catches sensitive information before it
            reaches the AI. Full audit logging for compliance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Outcome</div>
          <p class="text-muted">
            AI analytics without compliance risk. Passed security review in 2 weeks.
            Full audit trail satisfies regulatory requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section text-center">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h2 class="mb-md">Which describes you?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-xl">
        Tell us about your use case and we'll help you get started.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-md" style="justify-content: center;">
        <a href="https://app.getanswerlayer.com/sign-up" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="mailto:josh@getanswerlayer.com" class="btn btn-secondary">Talk to Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
